Name: Wooden Cot with Swinging Cradle
Description:
A Baby cot offers a perfectly comfortable and safe space for babies to catch their baby slumber. The Baby Bucket Wooden Cot with Swinging Cradle is an affordable baby cot that helps babies sleep safely in a cot or cradle as and when required. The Swinging cradle provides a rocking motion that helps babies sleep deeper. The cot and cradle come with wheels that can lock when stationary and can be released when needs to be transported. The Cot and cradle come with mosquito nets to protect from flying insects. The Wooden cot is an amazing addition to your or your baby's bedroom.

Features:

  • Cute Baby Cot and Cradle
  • Comes with safety wheel locking
  • Can be transported easily
  • Comes with mosquito net
  • Can be attached to bed safely

Size:

  • Cot Size: L115 x W68 x H 98cm
  • Cradle Size: L 100 X W 50 X H 45 cm

Age: 0 to 6 years (upto 30kgs)

Wash Care:
